    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Domini. Stat me domnus <persName><name ref="Andreas"
                                >Andreas</name></persName> reverentissimus <rs key="#Other_clerics"
                            >clericus</rs> et <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/1471">sancte <placeName
                                ref="#places/594">Ravennatis</placeName> Ecclesie</orgName> et <rs
                            key="#Abbots">abbas</rs>
                        <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterii</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries">Sancti Theodoris Christi martiris</orgName>
                        accepisse accepit ad te <persName key="#Abbots" ref="#people/1574"
                            >Vuido</persName> prudentissimus et <rs key="#Abbots">abbas</rs>
                        <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterii</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/1460">Sancte Marie que
                            vocatur a <placeName ref="#places/4179">Pomposia</placeName></orgName>
                        pensionem per <rs key="#Fundi">tres fundorum</rs> quorum vocabula sunt
                            <geogName key="#Fundi" ref="#estates/2475"><placeName key="#Fundi"
                                >Fabricianellus</placeName></geogName> et <geogName key="#Fundi"
                            ref="#estates/2476"><placeName key="#Fundi"
                            >Bethuli</placeName></geogName> et <geogName key="#Fundi"
                            ref="#estates/2477"><placeName>Sablune</placeName></geogName> et <rs
                            key="#Wine">quatuor vinee</rs> principales integre que sunt posite in
                            <rs key="#Fundi">fundum</rs> qui vocatur <geogName key="#Fundi #Wine"
                            ref="#estates/2478"><placeName key="#Fundi #Wine"
                                >Finciatiquo</placeName></geogName> quoerente se et cum omnibus sibi
                        pertinentibus, sitas <rs key="#Fines">territorio</rs>
                        <geogName key="#Fines" ref="#estates/2410"><placeName key="#Fines"
                                ref="#places/80">Ferrariensis</placeName></geogName>, <rs
                            key="#Plebs">plebis</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Plebs" ref="#juridical_persons/3612"><placeName
                                ref="#places/3598">Sancti Donati</placeName></orgName>, que vos per
                        paginam pacti tenere videtur iuris prefati monasterii, pro transacti
                        indicionibus usque in ista presentem indicione et per unaquamque indicionem
                            <rs key="#Rent_in_money">denariorum Venetiquorum triginta et sexto</rs>.
                        Unde pro munimine vestro fecit vobis hoc deaccepto in mense marti pro
                        transacto mense marcio pro indicione tertia, Ravenne. Ego Andreas clericus
                        sancte Ravennatis Ecclesie et abbas monasterii Sancti Theodori in hac die
                        subscripsi per indictionem tertiam. Ego Andreas clericus sancte Ravennatis
                        Ecclesie et abbas monasterii Sancti Theodori in hac die subscripsi per
                        indictionem quartam. </ab>
                </div>
